<!--
This configuration is expected to be placed in the devvm's /opt/ directory in order to be consumed 
by the libMiddlewareParameterService.so library. If this config does not exist, the built in groups 
will be used. The built in groups match this configuration exactly. The recommendation is to make a 
copy of this file and edit it to the user's needs.
The attributes are:
[domain]
    {name}: The domain name
    {id}: The domain id
[parameter]
    {name}: The name of the parameter
    {value_type}: The following values are allowed:
                    - numeric
                    - string
                    - binary

DISCLAIMER:
    This file does not get validated in anyway by the libMiddlewareParameterService.so library.
    Decision making is purely based on whether /opt/PARAMETER_SERVICE_TEST_MODE.xml exists.
-->
